{"id":44,"parent_id":0,"book_id":22563,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":44,"title":"“As Thou Hast Testified of Me in Jerusalem, so Must Thou Bear Witness Also at Rome”","subtitle":"","short_title":42,"uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.head1"},[".titleNumber","42"],["h1","“As Thou Hast Testified of Me in Jerusalem, so Must Thou Bear Witness Also at Rome”"]],[".bodyBlock",[".topic",["h2","Theme"],["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p4"},"The Lord will strenghthen and inspire those who courageously seek to declare his message in conditions of adversity."]],[".topic",["h2","Theme Analysis"],["div",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.f1"},["ul.content-list alphaCaps",["li",["span.label","A."],["div",[".para","Often we are confronted by people who try to turn us from our spiritual commitment."],["div",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.f2"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","1."],[".para","They tempt us to sin."]],["li",["span.label","2."],[".para","Using ridicule or threats, they try to keep us from defending the kingdom and its laws."]],["li",["span.label","3."],[".para","They try to get us to abandon or shirk good works."]]]]]],["li",["span.label","B."],["div",[".para","Our defense is moral and physical courage."]]],["li",["span.label","C."],["div",[".para","A true Christian’s courage grows out of his convictions about Christ, his loyalty to Him, his practice of Christ’s laws and programs, and the long-term perspective he gains by concentrating on future heavenly things."]]]]]],[".topic",["h2","Study Sources"],[".topic",["h3","New Testament Reading Assignment"],["div",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.18"},"Acts 21:18"],"through",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/28.31"},"28:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col"},"Colossians"]]],[".topic",["h3","Course Manual"],["div",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p16"},"Chapter 42, “As Thou Hast Testified of Me in Jerusalem, so Must Thou Bear Witness Also at Rome”"]],[".topic",["h3","Standard Works"],["div",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/3.7"},"1 Nephi 3:7"],". (See also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/3"},"chapters 3 through 5"],".) Why didn’t the Lord make it easy for Nephi to live up to his commitments?"],["div",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p19"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.1-10"},"Jacob 2:1-10"],". Why would it take courage for Jacob to deliver this message?"],["div",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/7.1-20"},"Jacob 7:1-20"],". The story of one who ridiculed a brave man of God."],["div",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p21"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/17"},"Mosiah 17"],". What kept Abinadi true to his trust?"],["div",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/21"},"Mosiah 21"],". What would it have taken to escape the persecution of wicked men?"],["div",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p23"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.10-13"},"Acts 21:10-13"],". It takes special courage to go deliberately on a dangerous errand."],["div",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.30"},"Acts 21:30"],"through",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.24"},"22:24"],". A testimony borne in chains."],["div",{"id":"p25","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p25"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.12-21"},"Acts 23:12-21"],". How determined were Paul’s enemies?"],["div",{"id":"p26","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p26"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.11"},"Acts 23:11"],". Good news and bad news."]],[".topic",["h3","Basic Library"],["div",{"id":"p28","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p28"},["span.emphasis","Gos. Doc,"],"pp. 530-34. Examples of the courage of President Joseph F. Smith."],["div",{"id":"p29","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p29"},"Harold B. Lee in",["span.emphasis","CR,"],"Oct. 1972, pp. 123-31. Where do we look for guidance on conduct and doctrine?"],["div",{"id":"p30","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p30"},["span.emphasis","Teachings,"],"pp. 155-57. Keys to avoiding apostasy."],["div",{"id":"p31","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p31"},["span.emphasis","Teachings,"],"p. 180. A description of Paul by one who saw him."],["div",{"id":"p32","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p32"},["span.emphasis","Teachings,"],"p. 225. What kind of men have been a problem in the former-day church as well as in the latter-day church?"],["div",{"id":"p33","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p33"},["span.emphasis","Discourses,"],"pp. 275-76. What is the effect of lack of confidence?"],["div",{"id":"p34","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p34"},["span.emphasis","Discourses,"],"p. 347. How should we meet our trials in doing the work of the Lord?"]],[".topic",["h3","Additional Sources"],["div",{"id":"p36","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p36"},"Gordon B. Hinckley in",["span.emphasis","CR,"],"Apr. 1966, p. 87. Elder Hinckley gives three keys to avoid being led astray."],["div",{"id":"p37","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p37"},"Parley P. Pratt,",["span.emphasis","Autobiography of Parley P. Pratt,"],"p. 192. This records a manifestation to Joseph Smith like Paul had in prison."],["div",{"id":"p38","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p38"},"Richard L. Evans,",["span.emphasis","From Within These Walls,"],"pp. 77-78. It takes character to carry responsibility."],["div",{"id":"p39","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p39"},"Orson Hyde in",["span.emphasis","Journal of Discourses,"],"1:125. He explains the terms in which the Lord intervenes to help us."],["div",{"id":"p40","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p40"},"Leon R. Hartshorn, “John Taylor the Courageous,”",["span.emphasis","New Era,"],"Jan. 1972, pp. 27-29. Stories of a courageous modern missionary."]],[".topic",["h3","Media Suggestions"],[".topic",["h4","Filmstrips"],["div",{"id":"p43","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p43"},"(The life of Paul, 7)",["span.emphasis","A Testimony Disregarded"],"(15:22)"],["div",{"id":"p44","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p44"},"(The life of Paul, 8)",["span.emphasis","Enduring to the End"],"(15:22)"]]]],[".topic",["h2","Some Suggestions for Presentation"],[".subtitle","(Ideas Other Teachers Have Used)"],[".topic",["h3","Questions Which Stimulate Discussion"],["div",{"id":"p48","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p48"},"Question: Why is it that the Lord let Paul, Nephi, and many other great servants go through such great trials before rescuing them or giving them the solution to their problems?"],["div",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.f3"},["h3","Discussion Goals (what should come out of the discussion)"],["ol.number",["li",["span.label","1."],[".para","The servants of God should know enough about him and have enough faith to place themselves completely in his hands."]],["li",["span.label","2."],[".para","We cannot accomplish the work of the Lord without the kind of commitment demonstrated by Paul and Nephi."]],["li",["span.label","3."],[".para","If we have faith, we do not need to know the future but can proceed one step at a time."]],["li",["span.label","4."],[".para","If we really have faith, we will expect whatever happens to be the best for us and for the work of the kingdom. (See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.3"},"D&C 98:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.15"},"100:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.25"},"Romans 8:25"],".)"]],["li",["span.label","5."],[".para","We cannot grow spiritually without having to overcome obstacles and hardships."]]]],["div",{"id":"p55","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p55"},"Question: Why does it take courage to resist false doctrine and temptation?"],["div",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.f4"},["h3","Discussion Goals"],["ol.number",["li",["span.label","1."],[".para","Sometimes there are implied threats of physical harm or economic or social reprisal. (What is economic reprisal? Answer: Loss of a job status if you don’t conform to a certain life-style. What is social reprisal? Answer: Exclusion from the group, and so forth.)"]],["li",["span.label","2."],[".para","Ridicule attacks the victim’s self-image. (For example, “You’re stupid! All scientists believe you are wrong!”) Often it is easier to recover from physical pain than from psychological damage or social rejection."]]]],["div",{"id":"p59","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p59"},"Question: What is the source of courage?"],["div",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.f5"},["h3","Discussion Goals"],["ol.number",["li",["span.label","1."],[".para","A correct knowledge of God leads to faith."]],["li",["span.label","2."],[".para","Others. (What other goals can be reached in such a discussion?)"]]]],["div",{"id":"p63","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p63"},"Question: What do personal purity and obedience have to do whith courage in declaring God’s message?"],["div",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.f6"},["ol.number",["li",["span.label","1."],[".para","A smoker, for example, cannot present the Word of Wisdom with the same conviction as a nonsmoker."]],["li",["span.label","2."],[".para","Others. (The teacher should have discussion goals in mind or on paper for all discussion questions. Otherwise the discussion will become aimless.)"]]]]],[".topic",["h3","A Chalkboard List of Synonyms and Antonyms"],"Instructors may wish to emphasize the need and nature of courage and faith in promulgating the gospel by showing the relationships which develop out of words in a list such as this:",["ul.noMarker",["li",[".para","Courage"]],["li",[".para","Faith"]],["li",[".para","Positive self-image"]],["li",[".para","Others"]],["li",[".para","Cowardice"]],["li",[".para","Doubt"]],["li",[".para","Negative self-image"]],["li",[".para","Others"]]]],[".topic",["h3","Parallels Between Colossians and Conference Reports"],["div",{"id":"p77","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/as-thou-hast-testified-of-me-in-jerusalem-so-must-thou-bear-witness-also-at-rome.p77"},"The instructor may wish to show how the teachings of Colossians are equally applicable to our day. This could be done by listing on a handout or on the chalkboard some of the warnings and teachings of Colossians and then reading excerpts from the recent",["span.emphasis","Conference Reports."],"(See, for example, Harold B. Lee in",["span.emphasis","CR,"],"Oct. 1972, pp. 59-65, 123-32.)"]]]]],"refs":null}
